Detailed Description

The Geometric Element types that can potentially be generated by Gambit are as follows (for each, we say if we support the mesh reading):

1D: Edge, 2 nodes Edge, 3 nodes (supported)

2D: Quadrilateral: 4 nodes Quadrilateral: 8 nodes Quadrilateral: 9 nodes (supported) Triangle: 3 nodes Triangle: 6 nodes (supported)

3D: Hexahedron: 8 nodes Hexahedron: 20 nodes Hexahedron: 27 nodes (supported) Tetrahedron: 4 nodes Tetrahedron: 10 nodes (supported) Wedge: 6 nodes Wedge: 15 nodes Wedge: 18 nodes (supported) Pyramid: 5 nodes Pyramid: 13 nodes Pyramid: 14 nodes

This class is useful to handle multilevel variables. It's going to be split into meshvariables and solutionvariables

Given the non linear problem 

 \Delta^2 u  = f(x),
 u(\Gamma) = 0
 \Delta u(\Gamma) = 0

in the unit box \Omega centered in the origin with boundary \Gamma, where 

                 f(x) = \Delta^2 u_e ,
               u_e = \cos ( \pi * x ) * \cos( \pi * y ),

the following function assembles the system: 

 \Delta u = v
 \Delta v = f(x) = 4. \pi^4 u_e
 u(\Gamma) = 0
 v(\Gamma) = 0

using automatic differentiation

◆ AssemblePoissonProblem_old_fe_quadrature_AD()

void femus::AssemblePoissonProblem_old_fe_quadrature_AD ( MultiLevelProblem &  ml_prob,
double(*)(const std::vector< double > &)  right_hand_side,
double(*)(const std::vector< double > &)  exact_solution 
)

This function assemble the stiffnes matrix KK and the residual vector Res Using automatic differentiation for Newton iterative scheme J(u0) w = - F(u0) , with u = u0 + w

  • F = f(x) - J u = Res J = \grad_u F

thus J w = f(x) - J u0

check the sign here

205 }

245 // define the dependent variables

247 s.dependent(&aResV[k][0], nDofsV);
248 }
249 s.dependent(&aResP[0], nDofsP);
250
251 // define the independent variables
252 for (unsigned k = 0; k < dim; k++) {
253 s.independent(&solV[k][0], nDofsV);
254 }
255 s.independent(&solP[0], nDofsP);
256
257 // get the and store jacobian matrix (row-major)
258 s.jacobian(&Jac[0] , true);

260

262 s.clear_dependents();
263 }

◆ compute_L2_norm_of_errors_of_unknowns_with_analytical_sol()

template<class real_num >
void femus::compute_L2_norm_of_errors_of_unknowns_with_analytical_sol ( MultiLevelProblem &  ml_prob,
const unsigned int  level_in,
const unsigned int  system_size_in 
)

@assignment You need to evaluate your manufactured right hand side at the quadrature point qp. Hence, you need to compute the coordinates of the quadrature point. Let us call them x_qp. These are obtained just like every quantity at a quadrature point, i.e., by interpolating the values of the quantity at the element nodes. The interpolation is performed by using the shape functions. In other words, (x_qp) = summation of (x_nodes) * (shape function of that node, evaluated at qp)

(x_nodes) are obtained from geom_element.get_coords_at_dofs_3d() (this is a std::vector < vector >, where the outer index is the dimension and the inner index ranges over the nodes) (shape function of that node, evaluated at qp) is obtained from phi_u (this is a vector, whose index ranges over the nodes)

284 mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face, igs, jacobian, phi, gradphi, normal);
285
286 // *** phi_i loop ***
287 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
288 adept::adouble value = -phi[i] * tau / rhof * jacobian;
289 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
290
291 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
292 if ((!solidmark[ilocal])) { //if fluid node it goes to U, V, W
293 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += value * normal[idim];
294 }
295 else { //if solid node it goes to DX, DY, DZ
296 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal] += value * normal[idim];
297 }
298 }
299 }
300 }
301 }
302 }
303 }
304 }
305
306 // *** Gauss point loop ***
307 double area = 1.;
308 adept::adouble supg_tau;
309
310 for (unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++) {
311 // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
312 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx, ig, jacobian, phi, gradphi, nablaphi);
313 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_hat, ig, jacobian_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat);
314 phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi(ig);
315
316 if (flag_mat == 2 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
317 if (ig == 0) {
318 double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight(ig);
319 area = jacobian_hat / GaussWeight;
320
321 if (iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
322 area_elem_first->add(mymsh->processor_id(), area);
323 area_elem_first->close();
324 rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
325 }
326 }
327
328 jacobianOverArea = jacobian_hat / area * rapresentative_area;
329 }
330
331 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
332 // displacement and velocity
333 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
334 SolVAR[i] = 0.;
335
336 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
337 GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
338 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
339 }
340
341 for (int j = 0; j < 3 * (dim - 1); j++) {
342 NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
343 NablaSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
344 }
345
346 for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++) {
347 SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
348
349 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
350 GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
351 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
352 }
353
354 for (int j = 0; j < 3 * (dim - 1); j++) {
355 NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * 3 * (dim - 1) + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
356 NablaSolhatVAR[i][j] += nablaphi_hat[inode * 3 * (dim - 1) + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
357 }
358 }
359 }
360
361 // pressure
362 SolVAR[2 * dim] = 0.;
363
364 for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++) {
365 adept::adouble soli = Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
366 SolVAR[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * soli;
367 }
368
369 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
370 //BEGIN FLUID ASSEMBLY
371 if (flag_mat == 2) {
372 //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
373 {
374 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
375
376 //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
377 adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
378
379 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
380 for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
381 LapmapVAR[idim] += (GradSolhatVAR[idim][jdim] * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim]) ;
382 }
383 }
384
385 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
386 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (!solidmark[i]) * (-LapmapVAR[idim] * jacobianOverArea);
387 }
388
389 //END redidual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
390
391 //BEGIN redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
392 adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
393 adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
394
395 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
396 for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
397 //LapvelVAR[idim] += GradSolVAR[dim+idim][jdim]*gradphi[i*dim+jdim];
398 LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
399 AdvaleVAR[idim] += SolVAR[dim + jdim] * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] * phi[i];
400 }
401 }
402
403 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
404 adept::adouble value = (-AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
405 - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
406 + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
407 ) * jacobian;
408
409 if ((!solidmark[i])) {
410 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value;
411 }
412 else {
413 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += value;
414 }
415
416 //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
417 }
418 }
419 }
420 //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
421
422 //BEGIN continuity block
423 {
424 adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
425
426 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
427 div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
428 }
429
430 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
431 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * div_vel) * jacobian;
432 }
433 }
434 //END continuity block
435 }
436 //END FLUID ASSEMBLY
437
438 //*******************************************************************************************************
439
440 //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY
441 else {
442
443
444 //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
445 //physical quantity
446 adept::adouble J_hat;
447 adept::adouble I_e;
448 adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
449 adept::adouble Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
450
451 adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
452 adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
453
454 if (solid_model == 0) { // Saint-Venant
455 adept::adouble e[3][3];
456
457 //computation of the stress tensor
458 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
459 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
460 e[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i]);
461 }
462 }
463
464 I_e = 0;
465
466 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
467 I_e += e[i][i];
468 }
469
470 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
471 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
472 //incompressible
473 Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2. * (incompressible) * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
474 //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
475 }
476 }
477 }
478
479 else { // hyperelastic non linear material
480 adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
481 adept::adouble B[3][3];
482
483 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
484 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
485 F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
486 }
487 }
488
489 J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
490 - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
491
492 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
493 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
494 B[I][J] = 0.;
495
496 for (int K = 0; K < 3; ++K) {
497 //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
498 B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
499 }
500 }
501 }
502
503 if (solid_model <= 4) { // Neo-Hookean
504 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
505
506 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
507 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
508 if (1 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * B[I][J]
509 - (incompressible) * mus * I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
510 else if (2 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus / J_hat * B[I][J]
511 - (incompressible) * mus / J_hat * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
512 else if (3 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) / J_hat
513 + lambda / J_hat * log(J_hat) * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
514 else if (4 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - I1_B * Id2th[I][J] / 3.) / pow(J_hat, 5. / 3.)
515 + lambda * (J_hat - 1.) * Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
516
517 }
518 }
519 }
520 else if (5 == solid_model) { //Mooney-Rivlin
521 adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2])
522 - B[0][1] * (B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0])
523 + B[0][2] * (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]);
524 adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
525 adept::adouble invB[3][3];
526
527 invB[0][0] = (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2]) * invdetB;
528 invB[1][0] = -(B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
529 invB[2][0] = (B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
530 invB[0][1] = -(B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
531 invB[1][1] = (B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
532 invB[2][1] = -(B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2]) * invdetB;
533 invB[0][2] = (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
534 invB[1][2] = -(B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
535 invB[2][2] = (B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
536
537 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
538 I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
539 - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
540
541 double C1 = mus / 3.;
542 double C2 = C1 / 2.;
543
544 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
545 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
546 Cauchy[I][J] = 2.*(C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J])
547 //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
548 - (incompressible) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
549 }
550 }
551
552 }
553 }
554
555 //END build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
556
557 //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
558 {
559 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
560
561 //BEGIN redidual v=0 in fixed domain
562 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
563 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += (-phi[i] * (-SolVAR[dim + idim])) * jacobian_hat;
564 }
565
566 //END redidual v=0 in fixed domain
567
568 //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
569 adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
570
571 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
572 for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
573 CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
574 }
575 }
576
577 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
578 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (phi[i] * _gravity[idim] - CauchyDIR[idim]) * jacobian;
579 }
580
581 //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
582 }
583 }
584 //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
585
586 //BEGIN continuity block
587 {
588 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
589
590 if (!penalty) {
591
592 if (0 == solid_model) {
593 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (I_e + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
594 }
595 else if (1 == solid_model || 5 == solid_model) {
596 if (incompressible) aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += phi1[i] * (J_hat - 1. + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim]) * jacobian_hat;
597// else aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += /*phi1[i]*/ /** 1.e10 */ SolVAR[2 * dim];
598 else aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i];
599 }
600 else if (2 == solid_model) {
601 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (log(J_hat) / J_hat + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
602 }
603
604 }
605 else {
606 if (3 == solid_model || 4 == solid_model) { // pressure = 0 in the solid
607 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += - ( -phi1[i] * (SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
608 }
609
610 }
611 }
612 }
613 //END continuity block
614 }
615
616 //END SOLID ASSEMBLY
617 }
618
619 //BEGIN local to global assembly
620 //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
621 for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
622 Rhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
623
624 for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
625 Rhs[indexVAR[i]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[i]][j].value();
626 }
627 }
628
629 Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
630
631 for (unsigned j = 0; j < nve1; j++) {
632 Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j].value();
633 }
634
635 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++) {
636 myRES->add_vector_blocked(Rhs[indexVAR[i]], dofsVAR[i]);
637 }
638
639 if( assembleMatrix ){
640 //Store equations
641 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
642 s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
643 s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
644 }
645
646 s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
647 s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
648
649 Jac.resize((2 * dim * nve + nve1) * (2 * dim * nve + nve1));
650
651 s.jacobian(&Jac[0], true);
652
653 myKK->add_matrix_blocked(Jac, dofsAll, dofsAll);
654 s.clear_independents();
655 s.clear_dependents();
656
657 //END local to global assembly
658 }
659 } //end list of elements loop
660
661 if( assembleMatrix ) myKK->close();
662 myRES->close();
663
664 delete area_elem_first;
665
666 // *************************************
667 end_time = clock();
668 AssemblyTime += (end_time - start_time);
669 // ***************** END ASSEMBLY RESIDUAL + MATRIX *******************
670
671 }

805 indVAR[ivar] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[ivar][0]);
806 indVAR[ivar + dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
807 SolType[ivar] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[ivar][0]);
808 SolType[ivar + dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
809 indexVAR[ivar] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[ivar][0]);
810 indexVAR[ivar + dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
811 }
812
813 indexVAR[2 * dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[6][0]);
814 indVAR[2 * dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[6][0]);
815 SolType[2 * dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[6][0]);
816 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
817
818 int nprocs = mymsh->n_processors();
819 NumericVector* area_elem_first;
820 area_elem_first = NumericVector::build().release();
821
822 if (nprocs == 1) {
823 area_elem_first->init(nprocs, 1, false, SERIAL);
824 }
825 else {
826 area_elem_first->init(nprocs, 1, false, PARALLEL);
827 }
828
829 area_elem_first->zero();
830 double rapresentative_area = 1.;
831
832 start_time = clock();
833
834 if( assembleMatrix ) myKK->zero();
835
836 // *** element loop ***
837 for (int iel = mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]; iel < mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc + 1]; iel++) {
838
839 short unsigned ielt = mymsh->GetElementType(iel);
840 unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber(iel, SolType2);
841 unsigned nve1 = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber(iel, SolType1);
842 int flag_mat = mymsh->GetElementMaterial(iel);
843
844 // *******************************************************************************************************
845
846 //initialization of everything in common between fluid and solid
847
848 //Rhs
849 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
850 dofsVAR[i].resize(nve);
851 Soli[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
852 aRhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
853 }
854
855 dofsVAR[2 * dim].resize(nve1);
856 Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
857 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
858
859 dofsAll.resize(0);
860
861 // ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
862 // coordinates, solutions, displacement and velocity dofs
863
864 solidmark.resize(nve);
865
866 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
867 vx[i].resize(nve);
868 vx_hat[i].resize(nve);
869 }
870
871 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
872 unsigned iDof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType2);
873
874 // flag nodes on the fluid-solid interface
875 solidmark[i] = mymsh->GetSolidMark(iDof);
876
877 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
878 Soli[indexVAR[j]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j]])(iDof);
879 Soli[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j + dim]])(iDof);
880
881 aRhs[indexVAR[j]][i] = 0.;
882 aRhs[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = 0.;
883
884 //Fixed coordinates (Reference frame)
885 vx_hat[j][i] = (*mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[j])(iDof);
886 // displacement dofs
887 dofsVAR[j][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[j], indexVAR[j], i, iel);
888 // velocity dofs
889 dofsVAR[j + dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[j + dim], indexVAR[j + dim], i, iel);
890 }
891 }
892
893 // pressure dofs
894 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
895 unsigned iDof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType[2 * dim]);
896 dofsVAR[2 * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[2 * dim], indexVAR[2 * dim], i, iel);
897 Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[2 * dim]])(iDof);
898 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = 0.;
899 }
900
901 // compose the system dofs
902 for (int idim = 0; idim < 2 * dim; idim++) {
903 dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[idim].begin(), dofsVAR[idim].end());
904 }
905
906 dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].end());
907
908 if( assembleMatrix ) s.new_recording();
909
910 //Moving coordinates (Moving frame)
911 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
912 for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
913 vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][j];
914 }
915 }
916
917 // Boundary integral
918 {
919 double tau = 0.;
920 std::vector < adept::adouble> normal(dim, 0);
921
922 // loop on faces
923 for (unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber(iel); jface++) {
924 std::vector < double > xx(3, 0.);
925
926 // look for boundary faces
927 if (myel->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) < 0) {
928 unsigned int face = -(mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) + 1);
929
930 if ( !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "U", tau, face, 0.) && tau != 0.) {
931 unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber(iel, jface, SolType2);
932 const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType(iel, jface);
933
934 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
935 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
936 unsigned iDof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(ilocal, iel, 2);
937
938 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
939 vx_face[idim][i] = (*mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[idim])(iDof) + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
940 }
941 }
942
943 for (unsigned igs = 0; igs < mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); igs++) {
944 mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face, igs, jacobian, phi, gradphi, normal);
945
946 // *** phi_i loop ***
947 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
948 adept::adouble value = -phi[i] * tau / rhof * jacobian;
949 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
950
951 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
952 if ((!solidmark[ilocal])) { //if fluid node it goes to U, V, W
953 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += value * normal[idim];
954 }
955 else { //if solid node it goes to DX, DY, DZ
956 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += value * normal[idim];
957 }
958 }
959 }
960 }
961 }
962 }
963 }
964 }
965
966 // *** Gauss point loop ***
967 double area = 1.;
968 adept::adouble supg_tau;
969
970 for (unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++) {
971 // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
972 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx, ig, jacobian, phi, gradphi, nablaphi);
973 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_hat, ig, jacobian_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat);
974 phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi(ig);
975
976 if (flag_mat == 2 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
977 if (ig == 0) {
978 double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight(ig);
979 area = jacobian_hat / GaussWeight;
980
981 if (iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
982 area_elem_first->add(mymsh->processor_id(), area);
983 area_elem_first->close();
984 rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
985 }
986 }
987
988 jacobianOverArea = jacobian_hat / area * rapresentative_area;
989 }
990
991 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
992 // displacement and velocity
993 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
994 SolVAR[i] = 0.;
995
996 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
997 GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
998 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
999 }
1000
1001 for (int j = 0; j < 3 * (dim - 1); j++) {
1002 NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1003 NablaSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1004 }
1005
1006 for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++) {
1007 SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1008
1009 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1010 GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1011 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1012 }
1013
1014 for (int j = 0; j < 3 * (dim - 1); j++) {
1015 NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * 3 * (dim - 1) + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1016 NablaSolhatVAR[i][j] += nablaphi_hat[inode * 3 * (dim - 1) + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1017 }
1018 }
1019 }
1020
1021 // pressure
1022 SolVAR[2 * dim] = 0.;
1023
1024 for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++) {
1025 adept::adouble soli = Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
1026 SolVAR[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * soli;
1027 }
1028
1029 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1030 //BEGIN FLUID ASSEMBLY
1031 if (flag_mat == 2) {
1032 //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1033 {
1034 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1035
1036 //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
1037 adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1038
1039 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1040 for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1041 LapmapVAR[idim] += (GradSolhatVAR[idim][jdim] * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim]) ;
1042 }
1043 }
1044
1045 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1046 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (!solidmark[i]) * (-LapmapVAR[idim] * jacobianOverArea);
1047 }
1048
1049 //END redidual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
1050
1051 //BEGIN redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1052 adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1053 adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1054
1055 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1056 for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1057 //LapvelVAR[idim] += GradSolVAR[dim+idim][jdim]*gradphi[i*dim+jdim];
1058 LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1059 AdvaleVAR[idim] += SolVAR[dim + jdim] * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] * phi[i];
1060 }
1061 }
1062
1063 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1064 adept::adouble value = (-AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
1065 - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
1066 + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1067 ) * jacobian;
1068
1069 if ((!solidmark[i])) {
1070 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value;
1071 }
1072 else {
1073 aRhs[indexVAR[dim+idim]][i] += value;
1074 }
1075
1076 //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1077 }
1078 }
1079 }
1080 //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1081
1082 //BEGIN continuity block
1083 {
1084 adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
1085
1086 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1087 div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
1088 }
1089
1090 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
1091 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * div_vel) * jacobian;
1092 }
1093 }
1094 //END continuity block
1095 }
1096 //END FLUID ASSEMBLY
1097
1098 //*******************************************************************************************************
1099
1100 //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY
1101 else {
1102 //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
1103 //physical quantity
1104 adept::adouble J_hat;
1105 adept::adouble I_e;
1106 adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
1107 adept::adouble Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
1108
1109 adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
1110 adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
1111
1112 if (solid_model == 0) { // Saint-Venant
1113 adept::adouble e[3][3];
1114
1115 //computation of the stress tensor
1116 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1117 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1118 e[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i]);
1119 }
1120 }
1121
1122 I_e = 0;
1123
1124 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1125 I_e += e[i][i];
1126 }
1127
1128 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1129 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1130 //incompressible
1131 Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
1132 //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
1133 }
1134 }
1135 }
1136
1137 else { // hyperelastic non linear material
1138 adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1139 adept::adouble B[3][3];
1140
1141 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1142 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1143 F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
1144 }
1145 }
1146
1147 J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
1148 - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
1149
1150 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1151 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1152 B[I][J] = 0.;
1153
1154 for (int K = 0; K < 3; ++K) {
1155 //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
1156 B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
1157 }
1158 }
1159 }
1160
1161 if (solid_model <= 4) { // Neo-Hookean
1162 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
1163
1164 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1165 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1166 if (1 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * B[I][J]
1167 - mus * I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
1168 else if (2 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus / J_hat * B[I][J]
1169 - mus / J_hat * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
1170 else if (3 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) / J_hat
1171 + lambda / J_hat * log(J_hat) * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
1172 else if (4 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - I1_B * Id2th[I][J] / 3.) / pow(J_hat, 5. / 3.)
1173 + lambda * (J_hat - 1.) * Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
1174
1175 }
1176 }
1177 }
1178 else if (5 == solid_model) { //Mooney-Rivlin
1179 adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2])
1180 - B[0][1] * (B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0])
1181 + B[0][2] * (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]);
1182 adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
1183 adept::adouble invB[3][3];
1184
1185 invB[0][0] = (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2]) * invdetB;
1186 invB[1][0] = -(B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
1187 invB[2][0] = (B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
1188 invB[0][1] = -(B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
1189 invB[1][1] = (B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
1190 invB[2][1] = -(B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2]) * invdetB;
1191 invB[0][2] = (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
1192 invB[1][2] = -(B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
1193 invB[2][2] = (B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
1194
1195 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
1196 I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
1197 - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
1198
1199 double C1 = mus / 3.;
1200 double C2 = C1 / 2.;
1201
1202 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1203 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1204 Cauchy[I][J] = 2.*(C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J])
1205 //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1206 - SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1207 }
1208 }
1209
1210 }
1211 }
1212
1213 //END build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
1214
1215 //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
1216 {
1217 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1218
1219 //BEGIN redidual v=0 in fixed domain
1220 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1221 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (-phi[i] * (-SolVAR[dim + idim])) * jacobian_hat;
1222 }
1223
1224 //END redidual v=0 in fixed domain
1225
1226 //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
1227 adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1228
1229 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1230 for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1231 CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
1232 }
1233 }
1234
1235 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1236 aRhs[indexVAR[dim+idim]][i] += (phi[i] * _gravity[idim] - CauchyDIR[idim]) * jacobian;
1237 }
1238
1239 //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
1240 }
1241 }
1242 //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
1243
1244 //BEGIN continuity block
1245 {
1246 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
1247 if (!penalty) {
1248 if (0 == solid_model) {
1249 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (I_e + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
1250 }
1251 else if (1 == solid_model || 5 == solid_model) {
1252 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += phi1[i] * (J_hat - 1. + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim]) * jacobian_hat;
1253 }
1254 else if (2 == solid_model) {
1255 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (log(J_hat) / J_hat + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
1256 }
1257 }
1258 else if (3 == solid_model || 4 == solid_model) { // pressure = 0 in the solid
1259 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
1260 }
1261 }
1262 }
1263 //END continuity block
1264 }
1265
1266 //END SOLID ASSEMBLY
1267 }
1268
1269 //BEGIN local to global assembly
1270 //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
1271 for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
1272 Rhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
1273
1274 for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
1275 Rhs[indexVAR[i]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[i]][j].value();
1276 }
1277 }
1278
1279 Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
1280
1281 for (unsigned j = 0; j < nve1; j++) {
1282 Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j].value();
1283 }
1284
1285 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++) {
1286 myRES->add_vector_blocked(Rhs[indexVAR[i]], dofsVAR[i]);
1287 }
1288
1289 if( assembleMatrix ){
1290 //Store equations
1291 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
1292 s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
1293 s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
1294 }
1295
1296 s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
1297 s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
1298
1299 Jac.resize((2 * dim * nve + nve1) * (2 * dim * nve + nve1));
1300
1301 s.jacobian(&Jac[0], true);
1302
1303 myKK->add_matrix_blocked(Jac, dofsAll, dofsAll);
1304 s.clear_independents();
1305 s.clear_dependents();
1306
1307 //END local to global assembly
1308 }
1309 } //end list of elements loop
1310
1311 if( assembleMatrix ) myKK->close();
1312 myRES->close();
1313
1314 delete area_elem_first;
1315
1316 // *************************************
1317 end_time = clock();
1318 AssemblyTime += (end_time - start_time);
1319 // ***************** END ASSEMBLY RESIDUAL + MATRIX *******************
1320
1321 }

20 //pointers and references
21
22 //MonolithicFSINonLinearImplicitSystem& my_nnlin_impl_sys = ml_prob.get_system<MonolithicFSINonLinearImplicitSystem>("Fluid-Structure-Interaction");
23 TransientNonlinearImplicitSystem& my_nnlin_impl_sys = ml_prob.get_system<TransientNonlinearImplicitSystem>("Fluid-Structure-Interaction");
24 const unsigned level = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetLevelToAssemble();
25
26 MultiLevelSolution* ml_sol = ml_prob._ml_sol;
27 Solution* mysolution = ml_sol->GetSolutionLevel(level);
28
29 LinearEquationSolver* myLinEqSolver = my_nnlin_impl_sys._LinSolver[level];
30 Mesh* mymsh = ml_prob._ml_msh->GetLevel(level);
31 elem* myel = mymsh->el;
32 SparseMatrix* myKK = myLinEqSolver->_KK;
33 NumericVector* myRES = myLinEqSolver->_RES;
34
35 const unsigned dim = mymsh->GetDimension();
36 const unsigned max_size = static_cast< unsigned >(ceil(pow(3, dim)));
37
38 double theta = 0.5;
39
40 // local objects
41 std::vector<adept::adouble> SolVAR(2 * dim + 1);
42 std::vector<double> SolVAR_old(2 * dim + 1);
43
44 std::vector< std::vector < adept::adouble > > GradSolVAR(2 * dim);
45 std::vector< std::vector < double > > GradSolVAR_old(2 * dim);
46
47 std::vector< std::vector < adept::adouble > > GradSolhatVAR(2 * dim);
48 std::vector< std::vector < double > > GradSolhatVAR_old(2 * dim);
49
50 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
51 GradSolVAR[i].resize(dim);
52 GradSolVAR_old[i].resize(dim);
53
54 GradSolhatVAR[i].resize(dim);
55 GradSolhatVAR_old[i].resize(dim);
56 }
57
58 std::vector < bool> solidmark;
59 std::vector < double > phi;
60 std::vector < double > phi_hat;
61 std::vector < double > phi_old;
62 std::vector < adept::adouble> gradphi;
63 std::vector < double > gradphi_hat;
64 std::vector < double > gradphi_old;
65 std::vector < adept::adouble> nablaphi;
66 std::vector < double > nablaphi_hat;
67 std::vector < double > nablaphi_old;
68
69
70 phi.reserve(max_size);
71 solidmark.reserve(max_size);
72 phi_hat.reserve(max_size);
73 phi_old.reserve(max_size);
74
75 gradphi.reserve(max_size * dim);
76 gradphi_hat.reserve(max_size * dim);
77 gradphi_old.reserve(max_size * dim);
78
79 nablaphi.reserve(max_size * 3 * (dim - 1));
80 nablaphi_hat.reserve(max_size * 3 * (dim - 1));
81 nablaphi_old.reserve(max_size * 3 * (dim - 1));
82
83 const double* phi1;
84
85 adept::adouble Weight = 0.;
86 adept::adouble Weight_nojac = 0.;
87 double Weight_hat = 0.;
88 double Weight_old = 0.;
89
90 std::vector < std::vector < adept::adouble> > vx(dim);
91 std::vector < std::vector < double> > vx_hat(dim);
92 std::vector < std::vector < double> > vx_old(dim);
93
94 std::vector < std::vector < adept::adouble > > vx_face(dim);
95 std::vector < std::vector < double > > vx_face_old(dim);
96
97 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
98 vx[i].reserve(max_size);
99 vx_hat[i].reserve(max_size);
100 vx_old[i].reserve(max_size);
101
102 vx_face[i].resize(9);
103 vx_face_old[i].resize(9);
104 }
105
106 std::vector< std::vector< adept::adouble > > Soli(2 * dim + 1);
107 std::vector< std::vector< double > > Soli_old(2 * dim + 1);
108 std::vector< std::vector< int > > dofsVAR(2 * dim + 1);
109
110 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++) {
111 Soli[i].reserve(max_size);
112 Soli_old[i].reserve(max_size);
113 dofsVAR[i].reserve(max_size);
114 }
115
116 std::vector< std::vector< double > > Rhs(2 * dim + 1);
117 std::vector< std::vector< adept::adouble > > aRhs(2 * dim + 1);
118
119 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++) {
120 aRhs[i].reserve(max_size);
121 Rhs[i].reserve(max_size);
122 }
123
124
125 std::vector < int > dofsAll;
126 dofsAll.reserve(max_size * (2 + dim + 1));
127
128 std::vector < double > KKloc;
129 KKloc.reserve(dim * max_size * (2 * dim + 1)*dim * max_size * (2 * dim + 1));
130
131 std::vector < double > Jac;
132 Jac.reserve(dim * max_size * (2 * dim + 1)*dim * max_size * (2 * dim + 1));
133
134 // ------------------------------------------------------------------------
135 // Physical parameters
136 double rhof = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid>("Fluid").get_density();
137 double rhos = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid>("Solid").get_density() / rhof;
138 double mu_lame = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid>("Solid").get_lame_shear_modulus();
139 double lambda_lame = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid>("Solid").get_lame_lambda();
140 double mus = mu_lame / rhof;
141 double IRe = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid>("Fluid").get_IReynolds_number();
142 double lambda = lambda_lame / rhof;
143 double betans = 1.;
144 int solid_model = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid>("Solid").get_physical_model();
145
146 if (solid_model >= 2 && solid_model <= 4) {
147 std::cout << "Error! Solid Model " << solid_model << "not implemented\n";
148 abort();
149 }
150
151 bool incompressible = (0.5 == ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid>("Solid").get_poisson_coeff()) ? 1 : 0;
152 const bool penalty = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid>("Solid").get_if_penalty();
153
154 // gravity
155 double _gravity[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
156
157 double dt = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetIntervalTime();
158 double time = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetTime();
159 // -----------------------------------------------------------------
160 // space discretization parameters
161 unsigned SolType2 = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(ml_sol->GetIndex("U"));
162 unsigned SolType1 = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(ml_sol->GetIndex("P"));
163
164 // mesh and procs
165 unsigned nel = mymsh->GetNumberOfElements();
166 unsigned igrid = mymsh->GetLevel();
167 unsigned iproc = mymsh->processor_id();
168
169 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
170 //variable-name handling
171 const char varname[7][3] = {"DX", "DY", "DZ", "U", "V", "W", "P"};
172 std::vector <unsigned> indexVAR(2 * dim + 1);
173 std::vector <unsigned> indVAR(2 * dim + 1);
174 std::vector <unsigned> SolType(2 * dim + 1);
175
176 for (unsigned ivar = 0; ivar < dim; ivar++) {
177 indVAR[ivar] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[ivar][0]);
178 indVAR[ivar + dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
179 SolType[ivar] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[ivar][0]);
180 SolType[ivar + dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
181 indexVAR[ivar] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[ivar][0]);
182 indexVAR[ivar + dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
183 }
184
185 indexVAR[2 * dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[6][0]);
186 indVAR[2 * dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[6][0]);
187 SolType[2 * dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[6][0]);
188 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
189
190 int nprocs = mymsh->n_processors();
191 NumericVector* area_elem_first;
192 area_elem_first = NumericVector::build().release();
193
194 if (nprocs == 1) {
195 area_elem_first->init(nprocs, 1, false, SERIAL);
196 }
197 else {
198 area_elem_first->init(nprocs, 1, false, PARALLEL);
199 }
200
201 area_elem_first->zero();
202 double rapresentative_area = 1.;
203
204 start_time = clock();
205
206 myKK->zero();
207
208 // *** element loop ***
209 for (int iel = mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]; iel < mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc + 1]; iel++) {
210
211 short unsigned ielt = mymsh->GetElementType(iel);
212 unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber(iel, SolType2);
213 unsigned nve1 = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber(iel, SolType1);
214 int flag_mat = mymsh->GetElementMaterial(iel);
215
216 // *******************************************************************************************************
217
218 //initialization of everything is in common fluid and solid
219
220 //Rhs
221 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
222 dofsVAR[i].resize(nve);
223 Soli[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
224 Soli_old[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
225
226 aRhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
227 Rhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
228 }
229
230 dofsVAR[2 * dim].resize(nve1);
231 Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
232 Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
233 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
234 Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
235
236 dofsAll.resize(0);
237
238 KKloc.resize((2 * dim * nve + nve1) * (2 * dim * nve + nve1));
239 Jac.resize((2 * dim * nve + nve1) * (2 * dim * nve + nve1));
240
241 // ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
242 // coordinates, solutions, displacement, velocity dofs
243
244 solidmark.resize(nve);
245
246 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
247 vx[i].resize(nve);
248 vx_hat[i].resize(nve);
249 vx_old[i].resize(nve);
250 }
251
252 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
253 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType2);
254 // flag to know if the node "idof" lays on the fluid-solid interface
255 solidmark[i] = mymsh->GetSolidMark(idof); // to check
256
257 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
258 Soli[indexVAR[j]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j]])(idof);
259 Soli[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j + dim]])(idof);
260
261 Soli_old[indexVAR[j]][i] = (*mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j]])(idof);
262 Soli_old[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j + dim]])(idof);
263
264 aRhs[indexVAR[j]][i] = 0.;
265 aRhs[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = 0.;
266
267 //Fixed coordinates (Reference frame)
268 vx_hat[j][i] = (*mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[j])(idof);
269 // displacement dofs
270 dofsVAR[j][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[j], indexVAR[j], i, iel);
271 // velocity dofs
272 dofsVAR[j + dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[j + dim], indexVAR[j + dim], i, iel);
273 }
274 }
275
276 // pressure dofs
277 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
278 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType[2 * dim]);
279 dofsVAR[2 * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[2 * dim], indexVAR[2 * dim], i, iel);
280 Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[2 * dim]])(idof);
281 Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[2 * dim]])(idof);
282 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = 0.;
283 }
284
285 // build dof ccomposition
286 for (int idim = 0; idim < 2 * dim; idim++) {
287 dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[idim].begin(), dofsVAR[idim].end());
288 }
289
290 dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].end());
291
292 //if (igrid==gridn || !myel->GetRefinedElementIndex(iel) ) {
293
294 s.new_recording();
295
296 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
297 for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
298 vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][j];
299 vx_old[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][j];
300 }
301 }
302
303 // Boundary integral
304 {
305 double tau = 0.;
306 std::vector < adept::adouble> normal(dim, 0);
307 std::vector < double > normal_old(dim, 0);
308
309 // loop on faces
310 for (unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber(iel); jface++) {
311 std::vector< double > xx(dim, 0.);
312
313 // look for boundary faces
314 if (myel->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) < 0) {
315
316 unsigned int face = -(mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) + 1);
317
318 if (!ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "U", tau, face, time) && tau != 0.) {
319 double tau_old;
320 ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "U", tau_old, face, time - dt);
321 unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber(iel, jface, SolType2);
322 const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType(iel, jface);
323
324 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
325 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
326 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(ilocal, iel, 2);
327
328 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
329 vx_face[idim][i] = (*mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[idim])(idof) + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
330 vx_face_old[idim][i] = (*mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[idim])(idof) + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
331 }
332 }
333
334 for (unsigned igs = 0; igs < mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); igs++) {
335 mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face, igs, Weight, phi, gradphi, normal);
336 mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face_old, igs, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, normal_old);
337
338 //phi1 =mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetPhi(igs);
339 // *** phi_i loop ***
340 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
341 adept::adouble value = - phi[i] * tau / rhof * Weight;
342 double value_old = - phi[i] * tau_old / rhof * Weight_old;
343 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
344
345 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
346 if ((!solidmark[ilocal])) {
347 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += dt*(theta*value + (1. - theta)*value_old) * normal[idim];
348 }
349 else { //if interface node it goes to solid
350 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal] += dt*(theta*value + (1. - theta)*value_old) * normal[idim];
351 }
352 }
353 }
354 }
355 }
356 }
357 }
358 }
359
360 // *** Gauss point loop ***
361 double area = 1.;
362
363 for (unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++) {
364 // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
365 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx, ig, Weight, phi, gradphi, nablaphi);
366 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_hat, ig, Weight_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat);
367 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_old, ig, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, nablaphi_old);
368 phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi(ig);
369
370 if (flag_mat == 2 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
371 if (ig == 0) {
372 double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight(ig);
373 area = Weight_hat / GaussWeight;
374
375 if (iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
376 area_elem_first->add(mymsh->processor_id(), area);
377 area_elem_first->close();
378 rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
379 }
380 }
381
382 Weight_nojac = Weight / area * rapresentative_area;
383 }
384
385 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
386 // displacement and velocity
387 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
388 SolVAR[i] = 0.;
389 SolVAR_old[i] = 0.;
390
391 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
392 GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
393 GradSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
394
395 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
396 GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
397 }
398
399 for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++) {
400 SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
401 SolVAR_old[i] += phi_old[inode] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
402
403 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
404 GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
405 GradSolVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_old[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
406
407 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
408 GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
409 }
410 }
411 }
412
413 // pressure
414 SolVAR[2 * dim] = 0.;
415 SolVAR_old[2 * dim] = 0.;
416
417 for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++) {
418 SolVAR[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
419 SolVAR_old[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
420 }
421
422 // Lagrangian mesh velocity at t = time + dt/2
423 std::vector < adept::adouble > meshVel(dim);
424 std::vector < std::vector < adept::adouble > > GradMeshVel(dim);
425
426 for (unsigned i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
427 meshVel[i] = (SolVAR[i] - SolVAR_old[i]) / dt;
428 GradMeshVel[i].resize(dim);
429
430 for (unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
431 GradMeshVel[i][j] = (GradSolVAR[i][j] - GradSolVAR_old[i][j]) / dt;
432 }
433 }
434
435 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
436 //BEGIN FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
437 if (flag_mat == 2) {
438 //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
439 {
440 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
441
442 //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
443 adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
444
445 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
446 for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
447 LapmapVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
448 }
449 }
450
451 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
452 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (!solidmark[i]) * (- LapmapVAR[idim] * Weight_nojac);
453 }
454
455 //END redidual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
456
457 //BEGIN redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
458 adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
459 adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
460 adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
461 adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
462
463 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
464 for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
465
466 LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
467 LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
468
469 AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
470 + (GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
471 ) * phi[i];
472
473 AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
474 + (GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
475 ) * phi_old[i];
476 }
477 }
478
479 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
480
481 adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
482 - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
483
484 adept::adouble value = theta * dt * (
485 - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
486 - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
487 + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
488 ) * Weight; // at time t
489
490 adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * dt * (
491 - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
492 - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
493 + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
494 ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
495
496 if (!solidmark[i]) {
497 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
498 }
499 else {
500 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
501 }
502
503 //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
504 }
505 }
506 }
507 //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
508
509 //BEGIN continuity block
510 {
511 adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
512
513 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
514 div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
515 }
516
517 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
518 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * div_vel) * Weight;
519 }
520 }
521 //END continuity block ===========================
522 }
523 //END FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
524
525 //*******************************************************************************************************
526
527 //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
528 else {
529 //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
530 //physical quantity
531 adept::adouble J_hat;
532 double J_hat_old;
533 adept::adouble I_e;
534 double I_e_old;
535 adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
536 adept::adouble Cauchy_old[3][3];
537 double Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
538
539
540
541
542 if (solid_model == 0) { // Saint-Venant
543 adept::adouble e[3][3];
544 double e_old[3][3];
545
546 //computation of the stress tensor
547 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
548 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
549 e[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i]);
550 e_old[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR_old[j][i]);
551 }
552 }
553
554 I_e = 0;
555 I_e_old = 0;
556
557 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
558 I_e += e[i][i];
559 I_e_old += e_old[i][i];
560 }
561
562 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
563 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
564 //incompressible
565 Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
566 Cauchy_old[i][j] = 2 * mus * e_old[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e_old * SolVAR_old[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
567 //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
568 }
569 }
570 }
571
572 else { // hyperelastic non linear material
573
574 adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
575 adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
576
577 double I1_B_old = 0.;
578 double I2_B_old = 0.;
579
580 adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
581 adept::adouble B[3][3];
582
583 double F_old[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
584 double B_old[3][3];
585
586 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
587 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
588 F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
589 F_old[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j];
590 }
591 }
592
593 J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
594 - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
595
596 J_hat_old = F_old[0][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[2][2] + F_old[0][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[2][0]
597 + F_old[0][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[2][1] - F_old[2][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[0][2]
598 - F_old[2][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[0][0] - F_old[2][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[0][1];
599
600
601 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
602 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
603 B[I][J] = 0.;
604 B_old[I][J] = 0.;
605
606 for (int K = 0; K < 3; ++K) {
607 //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
608 B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
609 B_old[I][J] += F_old[I][K] * F_old[J][K];
610 }
611 }
612 }
613
614 if (solid_model <= 4) { // Neo-Hookean
615 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
616 I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
617
618 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
619 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
620 if (1 == solid_model) { //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
621 Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) - mus / 3.*I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
622 Cauchy_old[I][J] = mus * (B_old[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) - mus / 3.*I1_B_old * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
623 }
624
625// else if ( 2 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus/J_hat*B[I][J]
626// -mus/J_hat*SolVAR[2*dim]*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
627// else if ( 3 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J])/J_hat
628// + lambda/J_hat*log(J_hat)*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
629// else if ( 4 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - I1_B*Id2th[I][J]/3.)/pow(J_hat,5./3.)
630// + lambda*(J_hat-1.)*Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
631//
632 }
633 }
634 }
635 else if (5 == solid_model) { //Mooney-Rivlin
636 adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2])
637 - B[0][1] * (B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0])
638 + B[0][2] * (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]);
639
640 double detB_old = B_old[0][0] * (B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[2][1] * B_old[1][2])
641 - B_old[0][1] * (B_old[2][2] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0])
642 + B_old[0][2] * (B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1]);
643
644 adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
645 double invdetB_old = 1. / detB_old;
646 adept::adouble invB[3][3];
647 double invB_old[3][3];
648
649 invB[0][0] = (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
650 invB[1][0] = -(B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
651 invB[2][0] = (B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
652 invB[0][1] = -(B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
653 invB[1][1] = (B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
654 invB[2][1] = -(B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2]) * invdetB;
655 invB[0][2] = (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
656 invB[1][2] = -(B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
657 invB[2][2] = (B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
658
659 invB_old[0][0] = (B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1]) * invdetB_old;
660 invB_old[1][0] = -(B_old[0][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][1]) * invdetB_old;
661 invB_old[2][0] = (B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[1][1]) * invdetB_old;
662 invB_old[0][1] = -(B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0]) * invdetB_old;
663 invB_old[1][1] = (B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][0]) * invdetB_old;
664 invB_old[2][1] = -(B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][2]) * invdetB_old;
665 invB_old[0][2] = (B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1]) * invdetB_old;
666 invB_old[1][2] = -(B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][1]) * invdetB_old;
667 invB_old[2][2] = (B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][1]) * invdetB_old;
668
669
670 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
671 I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
672 - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
673
674 I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
675 I2_B_old = B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] + B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] + B_old[2][2] * B_old[0][0]
676 - B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][2];
677
678 double C1 = mus / 3.;
679 double C2 = C1 / 2.;
680
681 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
682 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
683 Cauchy[I][J] = 2.*(C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J])
684 //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
685 - SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
686
687 Cauchy_old[I][J] = 2.* (C1 * B_old[I][J] - C2 * invB_old[I][J])
688 //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B_old - C2 * I2_B_old) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
689 - SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
690
691 }
692 }
693
694 }
695 }
696
697 //END build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
698
699 //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
700 {
701 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
702
703 //BEGIN redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
704 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
705 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += - phi[i] * (-SolVAR[idim] + SolVAR_old[idim] +
706 dt * (theta*SolVAR[dim + idim] + (1. - theta)*SolVAR_old[dim + idim])
707 ) * Weight_hat;
708 }
709
710 //END redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
711
712 //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
713 adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
714 adept::adouble CauchyDIR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
715
716 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
717 for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
718 CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
719 CauchyDIR_old[idim] += gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy_old[idim][jdim];
720 }
721 }
722
723 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
724
725 adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(rhos * SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
726 - rhos * SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
727
728 adept::adouble value = theta * dt * (rhos * phi[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
729 - CauchyDIR[idim] // stress
730 ) * Weight; // at time t
731
732 adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * dt * (rhos * phi_old[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
733 - CauchyDIR_old[idim] // stress
734 ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
735
736 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
737 }
738
739 //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
740 }
741 }
742 //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
743
744 //BEGIN continuity block
745 {
746 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
747 if (!penalty) {
748 if (0 == solid_model) {
749 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (I_e + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * Weight_hat;
750 }
751 else if (1 == solid_model || 5 == solid_model) {
752 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += phi1[i] * (J_hat - 1. + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim]) * Weight_hat;
753 }
754
755// else if (2 == solid_model){
756// aRhs[indexVAR[2*dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i]*( log(J_hat)/J_hat + (!incompressible)/lambda*SolVAR[2*dim] ) )*Weight_hat;
757// }
758 }
759
760// else if (3 == solid_model || 4 == solid_model){ // pressure = 0 in the solid
761// aRhs[indexVAR[2*dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i]*( SolVAR[2*dim] ) )*Weight_hat;
762// }
763 }
764 }
765 //END continuity block
766 }
767
768 //END SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
769 }
770
771 //}
772
773 //BEGIN local to global assembly
774 //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
775 for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
776 for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
777 Rhs[indexVAR[i]][j] = aRhs[indexVAR[i]][j].value();
778 }
779 }
780
781 for (unsigned j = 0; j < nve1; j++) {
782 Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j] = aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j].value();
783 }
784
785 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++) {
786 myRES->add_vector_blocked(Rhs[indexVAR[i]], dofsVAR[i]);
787 }
788
789 //Store equations
790 for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
791 s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
792 s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
793 }
794
795 s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
796 s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
797 s.jacobian(&Jac[0]);
798 unsigned nveAll = (2 * dim * nve + nve1);
799
800 for (int inode = 0; inode < nveAll; inode++) {
801 for (int jnode = 0; jnode < nveAll; jnode++) {
802 KKloc[inode * nveAll + jnode] = -Jac[jnode * nveAll + inode];
803 }
804 }
805
806 myKK->add_matrix_blocked(KKloc, dofsAll, dofsAll);
807 s.clear_independents();
808 s.clear_dependents();
809
810 //END local to global assembly
811
812 } //end list of elements loop
813
814 myKK->close();
815 myRES->close();
816
817 delete area_elem_first;
818
819 // *************************************
820 end_time = clock();
821 AssemblyTime += (end_time - start_time);
822 // ***************** END ASSEMBLY RESIDUAL + MATRIX *******************
823 }

226 for ( int iel = mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]; iel < mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc + 1]; iel++ ) {
