228 short unsigned ielt = mymsh->GetElementType ( iel );
229 unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber ( iel, SolType2 );
230 unsigned nve1 = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber ( iel, SolType1 );
231 int flag_mat = mymsh->GetElementMaterial ( iel );
232 unsigned elementGroup = mymsh->GetElementGroup ( iel );
233
234 // *******************************************************************************************************
235
236 //initialization of everything is in common fluid and solid
237
238 //Rhs
239 for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
240 dofsVAR[i].resize ( nve );
241 Soli[indexVAR[i]].resize ( nve );
242 Soli_old[indexVAR[i]].resize ( nve );
243
244 aRhs[indexVAR[i]].resize ( nve );
245 // Rhs[indexVAR[i]].resize ( nve );
246 }
247
248 dofsVAR[2 * dim].resize ( nve1 );
249 Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize ( nve1 );
250 Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize ( nve1 );
251 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize ( nve1 );
252 // Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize ( nve1 );
253
254 dofsAll.resize ( 0 );
255
256 // KKloc.resize ( ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 ) * ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 ) );
257 Jac.resize ( ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 ) * ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 ) );
258
259 // ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
260 // coordinates, solutions, displacement, velocity dofs
261
262 solidmark.resize ( nve );
263
264 for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
265 vx[i].resize ( nve );
266 vx_hat[i].resize ( nve );
267 vx_old[i].resize ( nve );
268 }
269
270 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
271 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof ( i, iel, SolType2 );
272 // flag to know if the node "idof" lays on the fluid-solid interface
273 solidmark[i] = mymsh->GetSolidMark ( idof ); // to check
274
275 for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
276 Soli[indexVAR[j]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j]] ) ( idof );
277 Soli[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j + dim]] ) ( idof );
278
279 Soli_old[indexVAR[j]][i] = ( *mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j]] ) ( idof );
280 Soli_old[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j + dim]] ) ( idof );
281
282 aRhs[indexVAR[j]][i] = 0.;
283 aRhs[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = 0.;
284
285 //Fixed coordinates (Reference frame)
286 vx_hat[j][i] = ( *mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[j] ) ( idof );
287 // displacement dofs
288 dofsVAR[j][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[j], indexVAR[j], i, iel );
289 // velocity dofs
290 dofsVAR[j + dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[j + dim], indexVAR[j + dim], i, iel );
291 }
292 }
293
294 // pressure dofs
295 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
296 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof ( i, iel, SolType[2 * dim] );
297 dofsVAR[2 * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[2 * dim], indexVAR[2 * dim], i, iel );
298 Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[2 * dim]] ) ( idof );
299 Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[2 * dim]] ) ( idof );
300 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = 0.;
301 }
302
303 // build dof ccomposition
304 for ( int idim = 0; idim < 2 * dim; idim++ ) {
305 dofsAll.insert ( dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[idim].begin(), dofsVAR[idim].end() );
306 }
307
308 dofsAll.insert ( dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].end() );
309
310 //if (igrid==gridn || !myel->GetRefinedElementIndex(iel) ) {
311
312 if ( assembleMatrix ) s.new_recording();
313
314 for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
315 for ( int j = 0; j < nve; j++ ) {
316 vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][j];
317 vx_old[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][j];
318 }
319 }
320
321 //Boundary integral
322 {
323
324 std::vector < adept::adouble> normal ( dim, 0 );
325 std::vector < double > normal_old ( dim, 0 );
326
327 // loop on faces
328 for ( unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber ( iel ); jface++ ) {
329 std::vector< double > xx ( dim, 0. );
330
331 // look for boundary faces
332 if ( myel->GetFaceElementIndex ( iel, jface ) < 0 ) {
333
334 unsigned int face = - ( mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex ( iel, jface ) + 1 );
335 double tau = 0.;
336 double tau_old = 0.;
337 if ( ( !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction() ( xx, "P", tau, face, time ) &&
338 !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction() ( xx, "P", tau_old, face, time - dt ) )
339 && ( tau != 0. || tau_old != 0. ) ) {
340
341 unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber ( iel, jface, SolType2 );
342 const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType ( iel, jface );
343
344 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
345 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex ( iel, jface, i );
346 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof ( ilocal, iel, 2 );
347
348 for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
349 vx_face[idim][i] = ( *mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[idim] ) ( idof ) + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
350 vx_face_old[idim][i] = ( *mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[idim] ) ( idof ) + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
351 }
352 }
353
354 for ( unsigned igs = 0; igs < mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); igs++ ) {
355 mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur ( vx_face, igs, Weight, phi, gradphi, normal );
356 mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur ( vx_face_old, igs, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, normal_old );
357
358 //phi1 =mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetPhi(igs);
359 // *** phi_i loop ***
360 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
361 adept::adouble value = - phi[i] * tau / rhof * Weight;
362 double value_old = - phi_old[i] * tau_old / rhof * Weight_old;
363 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex ( iel, jface, i );
364
365 for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
366 if ( ( !solidmark[ilocal] ) ) {
367 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += ( theta * value + ( 1. - theta ) * value_old ) * normal[idim];
368 }
369 else { //if interface node it goes to solid
370 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal] += ( theta * value + ( 1. - theta ) * value_old ) * normal[idim];
371 }
372 }
373 }
374 }
375 }
376 }
377 }
378 }
379
380 // *** Gauss point loop ***
381 double area = 1.;
382
383 for ( unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++ ) {
384 // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
385 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx, ig, Weight, phi, gradphi, nablaphi );
386 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx_hat, ig, Weight_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat );
387 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx_old, ig, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, nablaphi_old );
388 phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi ( ig );
389
390 if ( flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc] ) {
391 if ( ig == 0 ) {
392 double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight ( ig );
393 area = Weight_hat / GaussWeight;
394
395 if ( iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc] ) {
396 area_elem_first->add ( mymsh->processor_id(), area );
397 area_elem_first->close();
398 rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
399 }
400 }
401
402 Weight_nojac = Weight / area * rapresentative_area;
403
404// std::vector<double> xc(dim,0.);
405// xc[0] = -0.001013;
406// xc[1] = 0.07000;
407// double distance = 0.;
408// for (unsigned k = 0; k<dim; k++){
409// distance += ( vx_hat[k][ nve - 1] - xc[k] ) * ( vx_hat[k][nve - 1] - xc[k] );
410// }
411// distance =sqrt(distance);
412// Weight_nojac *= 1./(1 + 10000 * distance);
413//
414// if(elementGroup == 16) Weight_nojac *= 1.e06;
415 }
416
417 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
418 // displacement and velocity
419 for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
420 SolVAR[i] = 0.;
421 SolVAR_old[i] = 0.;
422
423 for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
424 GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
425 GradSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
426
427 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
428 GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
429 }
430
431 for ( int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++ ) {
432 NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
433 NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
434 }
435
436 for ( unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++ ) {
437 SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
438 SolVAR_old[i] += phi_old[inode] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
439
440 for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
441 GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
442 GradSolVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_old[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
443
444 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
445 GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
446 }
447 for ( int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++ ) {
448 NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
449 NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] += nablaphi_old[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
450 }
451 }
452 }
453
454 // pressure
455 SolVAR[2 * dim] = 0.;
456
457 for ( unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++ ) {
458 SolVAR[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
459 }
460
461 // Lagrangian mesh velocity at t = time + dt/2
462 std::vector < adept::adouble > meshVel ( dim );
463 std::vector < std::vector < adept::adouble > > GradMeshVel ( dim );
464
465 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
466 meshVel[i] = ( SolVAR[i] - SolVAR_old[i] ) / dt;
467 GradMeshVel[i].resize ( dim );
468
469 for ( unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
470 GradMeshVel[i][j] = ( GradSolVAR[i][j] - GradSolVAR_old[i][j] ) / dt;
471 }
472 }
473
474 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
475 //BEGIN FLUID and POROUS MEDIA ASSEMBLY ============
476 if ( flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3 ) {
477
478 std::vector < adept::adouble > a ( dim );
479 std::vector < adept::adouble > a_old ( dim );
480 for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
481 a[i] = SolVAR[i + dim] - 0.*meshVel[i]; // TODO maybe we subtract meshVel[i] maybe not
482 a_old[i] = SolVAR_old[i + dim] - 0.*meshVel[i];
483 }
484
485 // speed
486 adept::adouble aL2Norm = 0.;
487 adept::adouble a_oldL2Norm = 0.;
488 for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
489 aL2Norm += a[i] * a[i];
490 a_oldL2Norm += a_old[i] * a_old[i];
491 }
492 aL2Norm = sqrt ( aL2Norm );
493 a_oldL2Norm = sqrt ( a_oldL2Norm );
494
495 double sqrtlambdak = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indLmbd] ) ( iel );
496 adept::adouble tauSupg = 1. / ( sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe );
497 adept::adouble tauSupg_old = 1. / ( sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe );
498 adept::adouble Rek = aL2Norm / ( 4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe );
499 adept::adouble Rek_old = a_oldL2Norm / ( 4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe );
500
501 if ( Rek > 1.0e-15 ) {
502 adept::adouble xiRek = ( Rek >= 1. ) ? 1. : Rek;
503 tauSupg = xiRek / ( aL2Norm * sqrtlambdak );
504 }
505
506 if ( Rek_old > 1.0e-15 ) {
507 adept::adouble xiRek_old = ( Rek_old >= 1. ) ? 1. : Rek_old;
508 tauSupg_old = xiRek_old / ( a_oldL2Norm * sqrtlambdak );
509 }
510
511 //std::cout << tauSupg.value() <<" " <<tauSupg_old.value()<<std::endl;
512
513
514 std::vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg ( nve, 0. );
515 std::vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg_old ( nve, 0. );
516 //tauSupg=0;
517 //tauSupg_old=0;
518 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
519 for ( unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
520 phiSupg[i] += ( ( SolVAR[j + dim] - meshVel[j] ) * gradphi[i * dim + j] ) * tauSupg;// * (!solidmark[i]) ;
521 phiSupg_old[i] += ( ( SolVAR_old[j + dim] - meshVel[j] ) * gradphi_old[i * dim + j] ) * tauSupg_old;// * (!solidmark[i]);
522 }
523 }
524
525
526 //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
527 {
528 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
529
530 //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
531 adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
532
533 for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
534 for ( int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
535 //LapmapVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] ) * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim];
536 LapmapVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] + 0.*GradSolVAR[jdim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
537 }
538 }
539
540 for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
541 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += ( !solidmark[i] ) * ( - LapmapVAR[idim] * Weight_nojac );
542 }
543
544 //END residual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
545
546 if ( flag_mat == 2 ) {
547 //BEGIN residual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
548 adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
549 adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
550 adept::adouble LapStrong[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
551 adept::adouble LapStrong_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
552 adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
553 adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
554
555 for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
556 for ( int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
557 unsigned kdim;
558 if ( idim == jdim ) kdim = jdim;
559 else if ( 1 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim; // xy
560 else if ( 2 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim + 2; // xz
561 else if ( 3 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim + 1; // yz
562 //laplaciano debole
563 LapvelVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
564 LapvelVAR_old[idim] += ( GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim] ) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
565 //laplaciano strong
566 LapStrong[idim] += ( NablaSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR[dim + jdim][kdim] ) * phiSupg[i];
567 LapStrong_old[idim] += ( NablaSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][kdim] ) * phiSupg_old[i];
568
569 AdvaleVAR[idim] += ( ( SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim] ) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
570 + ( 0.*GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim] ) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
571 //) * phi[i];
572 ) * ( phi[i] + phiSupg[i] );
573
574 AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ( ( SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim] ) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
575 + (0.*GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim] ) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
576 //) * phi_old[i];
577 ) * ( phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i] );
578 }
579 }
580
581 for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
582
583 adept::adouble timeDerivative = - ( SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( phi[i] + phiSupg[i] ) * Weight
584 - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i] ) * Weight_old )/dt;
585
586 adept::adouble value = theta * (
587 - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
588 - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
589 + IRe * LapStrong[idim]
590 + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
591 ) * Weight; // at time t
592
593 adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * (
594 - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
595 - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
596 + IRe * LapStrong_old[idim]
597 + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
598 ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
599
600 if ( !solidmark[i] ) {
601 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
602 }
603 else {
604 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
605 }
606
607 }
608 //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
609 }
610 else if ( flag_mat == 3 ) {
611 //BEGIN redidual Porous Media in moving domain
612
613
614 adept::adouble speed = 0.;
615 adept::adouble speed_old = 0.;
616 for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
617 speed += SolVAR[dim + idim] * SolVAR[dim + idim];
618 speed_old += SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * SolVAR_old[dim + idim];
619 }
620 double eps = 1.0e-12;
621 speed = sqrt ( speed + eps );
622 speed_old = sqrt ( speed_old + eps );
623 double DE = 0.;
624 if ( dim == 2 ) {
625 DE = 0.0002; // AAA_thrombus_2D
626 //DE = 0.00006; // turek2D
627 }
628 else if ( dim == 3 ) {
629 DE = 0.000112; // porous3D
630 }
631 double b = 4188;
632 double a = 1452;
633 double K = DE * IRe * rhof / b; // alpha = mu/b * De
634 double C2 = 2 * a / ( rhof * DE );
635
636
637
638
639
640// adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
641// adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
642// adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
643// adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
644//
645// for(int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
646// for(int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
647//
648// LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
649// LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
650//
651// AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
652// + (GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
653// ) * phi[i];
654//
655// AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
656// + (GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
657// ) * phi_old[i];
658// }
659// }
660
661 for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
662
663// adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
664// - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
665
666 adept::adouble value = theta * (
667// - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
668// - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
669 //- SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * phi[i]
670 - (SolVAR[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i])
671 + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
672 ) * Weight; // at time t
673
674 adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * (
675// - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
676// - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
677 //- SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed_old ) * phi_old[i]
678 - (SolVAR_old[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i])
679 + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
680 ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
681
682 if ( !solidmark[i] ) {
683 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value + value_old;
684 }
685 else {
686 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += value + value_old;
687 }
688
689 }
690 //END redidual Porous Media in moving domain
691 }
692 }
693 }
694 //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
695
696 //BEGIN continuity block
697 {
698 adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
699
700 for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
701 div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
702 }
703
704 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
705 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += - ( -phi1[i] * div_vel ) * Weight;
706 }
707 }
708 //END continuity block ===========================
709 }
710 //END FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
711
712 //*******************************************************************************************************
713
714 //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
715 else {
716 //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
717 //physical quantity
718 adept::adouble J_hat;
719 double J_hat_old;
720 adept::adouble I_e;
721 double I_e_old;
722 adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
723 adept::adouble Cauchy_old[3][3];
724 double Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
725
726
727
728
729 if ( solid_model == 0 ) { // Saint-Venant
730 adept::adouble e[3][3];
731 double e_old[3][3];
732
733 //computation of the stress tensor
734 for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
735 for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
736 e[i][j] = 0.5 * ( GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i] );
737 e_old[i][j] = 0.5 * ( GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR_old[j][i] );
738 }
739 }
740
741 I_e = 0;
742 I_e_old = 0;
743
744 for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
745 I_e += e[i][i];
746 I_e_old += e_old[i][i];
747 }
748
749 for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
750 for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
751 //incompressible
752 Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
753 Cauchy_old[i][j] = 2 * mus * e_old[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e_old * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
754 //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
755 }
756 }
757 }
758
759 else { // hyperelastic non linear material
760
761 adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
762 adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
763
764 double I1_B_old = 0.;
765 double I2_B_old = 0.;
766
767 adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
768 adept::adouble B[3][3];
769
770 double F_old[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
771 double B_old[3][3];
772
773 for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
774 for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
775 F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
776 F_old[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j];
777 }
778 }
779
780 J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
781 - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
782
783 J_hat_old = F_old[0][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[2][2] + F_old[0][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[2][0]
784 + F_old[0][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[2][1] - F_old[2][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[0][2]
785 - F_old[2][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[0][0] - F_old[2][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[0][1];
786
787
788 for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
789 for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
790 B[I][J] = 0.;
791 B_old[I][J] = 0.;
792
793 for ( int K = 0; K < 3; ++K ) {
794 //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
795 B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
796 B_old[I][J] += F_old[I][K] * F_old[J][K];
797 }
798 }
799 }
800
801 if ( solid_model <= 4 ) { // Neo-Hookean
802 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
803 I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
804
805 for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
806 for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
807 if ( 1 == solid_model ) { //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
808 Cauchy[I][J] = mus * ( B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J] ) - mus / 3.*I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
809 Cauchy_old[I][J] = mus * ( B_old[I][J] - Id2th[I][J] ) - mus / 3.*I1_B_old * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
810 }
811
812// else if ( 2 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus/J_hat*B[I][J]
813// -mus/J_hat*SolVAR[2*dim]*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
814// else if ( 3 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J])/J_hat
815// + lambda/J_hat*log(J_hat)*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
816// else if ( 4 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - I1_B*Id2th[I][J]/3.)/pow(J_hat,5./3.)
817// + lambda*(J_hat-1.)*Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
818//
819 }
820 }
821 }
822 else if ( 5 == solid_model ) { //Mooney-Rivlin
823 adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * ( B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2] )
824 - B[0][1] * ( B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0] )
825 + B[0][2] * ( B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1] );
826
827 double detB_old = B_old[0][0] * ( B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[2][1] * B_old[1][2] )
828 - B_old[0][1] * ( B_old[2][2] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0] )
829 + B_old[0][2] * ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1] );
830
831 adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
832 double invdetB_old = 1. / detB_old;
833 adept::adouble invB[3][3];
834 double invB_old[3][3];
835
836 invB[0][0] = ( B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] ) * invdetB;
837 invB[1][0] = - ( B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1] ) * invdetB;
838 invB[2][0] = ( B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1] ) * invdetB;
839 invB[0][1] = - ( B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0] ) * invdetB;
840 invB[1][1] = ( B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0] ) * invdetB;
841 invB[2][1] = - ( B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2] ) * invdetB;
842 invB[0][2] = ( B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1] ) * invdetB;
843 invB[1][2] = - ( B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1] ) * invdetB;
844 invB[2][2] = ( B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1] ) * invdetB;
845
846 invB_old[0][0] = ( B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] ) * invdetB_old;
847 invB_old[1][0] = - ( B_old[0][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][1] ) * invdetB_old;
848 invB_old[2][0] = ( B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[1][1] ) * invdetB_old;
849 invB_old[0][1] = - ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0] ) * invdetB_old;
850 invB_old[1][1] = ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][0] ) * invdetB_old;
851 invB_old[2][1] = - ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][2] ) * invdetB_old;
852 invB_old[0][2] = ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1] ) * invdetB_old;
853 invB_old[1][2] = - ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][1] ) * invdetB_old;
854 invB_old[2][2] = ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][1] ) * invdetB_old;
855
856
857 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
858 I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
859 - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
860
861 I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
862 I2_B_old = B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] + B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] + B_old[2][2] * B_old[0][0]
863 - B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][2];
864
865 //double C1 = mus / 3.;
866 double C1 = ( elementGroup == 15 ) ? mus1 / 3. : mus / 3.;
867 double C2 = C1 / 2.;
868
869 for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
870 for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
871 Cauchy[I][J] = 2.* ( C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J] )
872 //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
873 - 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
874
875 Cauchy_old[I][J] = 2.* ( C1 * B_old[I][J] - C2 * invB_old[I][J] )
876 //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B_old - C2 * I2_B_old) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
877 - 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
878
879 }
880 }
881
882 }
883 }
884
885 //END build Cauchy Stress in moving domain
886
887 //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
888 {
889 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
890
891 //BEGIN redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
892 for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
893 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += - phi[i] * ( (-SolVAR[idim] + SolVAR_old[idim])/dt +
894 ( theta * SolVAR[dim + idim] + ( 1. - theta ) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim] )
895 ) * Weight_hat;
896 }
897
898 //END redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
899
900 //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
901 adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
902 adept::adouble CauchyDIR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
903
904 for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
905 for ( int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
906 CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
907 CauchyDIR_old[idim] += gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy_old[idim][jdim];
908 }
909 }
910
911 for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
912
913 adept::adouble timeDerivative = - ( rhos * SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
914 - rhos * SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old )/dt;
915
916 adept::adouble value = theta * ( rhos * phi[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
917 - CauchyDIR[idim] // stress
918 ) * Weight; // at time t
919
920 adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * ( rhos * phi_old[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
921 - CauchyDIR_old[idim] // stress
922 ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
923
924 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
925 }
926
927 //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
928 }
929 }
930 //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
931
932 //BEGIN continuity block
933 {
934 for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
935 if ( !penalty ) {
936 if ( 0 == solid_model ) {
937 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += - ( -phi1[i] * ( I_e + ( !incompressible ) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim] ) ) * Weight_hat;
938 }
939 else if ( 1 == solid_model || 5 == solid_model ) {
940 aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += phi1[i] * ( J_hat - 1. + ( !incompressible ) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim] ) * Weight_hat;
941 }
942
943// else if (2 == solid_model){
944// aRhs[indexVAR[2*dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i]*( log(J_hat)/J_hat + (!incompressible)/lambda*SolVAR[2*dim] ) )*Weight_hat;
945// }
946 }
947
948// else if (3 == solid_model || 4 == solid_model){ // pressure = 0 in the solid
949// aRhs[indexVAR[2*dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i]*( SolVAR[2*dim] ) )*Weight_hat;
950// }
951 }
952 }
953 //END continuity block
954 }

956 //END SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
957 }

961 //BEGIN local to global assembly
962 //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
963 for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {

965

1229
1230 // ------------------------------------------------------------------------
1231 // Physical parameters
1232 double rhof = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid> ("Fluid").get_density();
1233 double rhos = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid> ("Solid").get_density() / rhof;
1234 double mu_lame = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ("Solid").get_lame_shear_modulus();
1235 double lambda_lame = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ("Solid").get_lame_lambda();
1236 double mus = mu_lame / rhof;
1237 double mu_lame1 = ml_prob.parameters.get < Solid> ("Solid1").get_lame_shear_modulus();
1238 double mus1 = mu_lame1 / rhof;
1239 double IRe = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid> ("Fluid").get_IReynolds_number();
1240 double lambda = lambda_lame / rhof;
1241 double betans = 1.;
1242 int solid_model = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ("Solid").get_physical_model();
1243
1244 if (solid_model >= 2 && solid_model <= 4) {
1245 std::cout << "Error! Solid Model " << solid_model << "not implemented\n";
1246 abort();
1247 }
1248
1249 bool incompressible = (0.5 == ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ("Solid").get_poisson_coeff()) ? 1 : 0;
1250 const bool penalty = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ("Solid").get_if_penalty();
1251
1252 // gravity
1253 double _gravity[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1254
1255 double dt = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetIntervalTime();
1256 double time = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetTime();
1257 // -----------------------------------------------------------------
1258 // space discretization parameters
1259 unsigned SolType2 = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(ml_sol->GetIndex("U"));
1260 unsigned SolType1 = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(ml_sol->GetIndex("PS"));
1261
1262 // mesh and procs
1263 unsigned nel = mymsh->GetNumberOfElements();
1264 unsigned igrid = mymsh->GetLevel();
1265 unsigned iproc = mymsh->processor_id();
1266
1267 unsigned indLmbd = ml_sol->GetIndex("lmbd");
1268
1269 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1270 //variable-name handling
1271 const char varname[10][4] = {"DX", "DY", "DZ", "U", "V", "W", "DX1", "DY1", "DZ1", "PS"};
1272
1273 std::vector <unsigned> indexVAR(nBlocks * dim + 1);
1274 std::vector <unsigned> indVAR(nBlocks * dim + 1);
1275 std::vector <unsigned> SolType(nBlocks * dim + 1);
1276
1277 for (unsigned ivar = 0; ivar < dim; ivar++) {
1278 for (unsigned k = 0; k < nBlocks; k++) {
1279 indVAR[ivar + k * dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[ivar + k * 3][0]);
1280 SolType[ivar + k * dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[ivar + k * 3][0]);
1281 indexVAR[ivar + k * dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[ivar + k * 3][0]);
1282 }
1283 }
1284
1285 indexVAR[nBlocks * dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[9][0]);
1286 indVAR[nBlocks * dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[9][0]);
1287 SolType[nBlocks * dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[9][0]);
1288 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1289
1290 int nprocs = mymsh->n_processors();
1291 NumericVector * area_elem_first;
1292 area_elem_first = NumericVector::build().release();
1293
1294 if (nprocs == 1) {
1295 area_elem_first->init(nprocs, 1, false, SERIAL);
1296 }
1297 else {
1298 area_elem_first->init(nprocs, 1, false, PARALLEL);
1299 }
1300
1301
1302 double rapresentative_area = 1.;
1303
1304 start_time = clock();
1305
1306 if (assembleMatrix) myKK->zero();
1307
1308 NumericVector* setIfCorrupted;
1309 setIfCorrupted = NumericVector::build().release();
1310 setIfCorrupted->init(mymsh->n_processors(), 1 , false, AUTOMATIC);
1311
1312
1313 begin:
1314
1315 area_elem_first->zero();
1316 setIfCorrupted->zero();
1317
1318 // *** element loop ***
1319 for (int iel = mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]; iel < mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc + 1]; iel++) {
1320
1321 short unsigned ielt = mymsh->GetElementType(iel);
1322 unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber(iel, SolType2);
1323 unsigned nve1 = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber(iel, SolType1);
1324 int flag_mat = mymsh->GetElementMaterial(iel);
1325 unsigned elementGroup = mymsh->GetElementGroup(iel);
1326
1327 // *******************************************************************************************************
1328
1329 //initialization of everything is in common fluid and solid
1330
1331 //Rhs
1332 for (int i = 0; i < nBlocks * dim; i++) {
1333 dofsVAR[i].resize(nve);
1334 Soli[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
1335 Soli_old[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
1336 aRhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
1337 }
1338
1339 dofsVAR[nBlocks * dim].resize(nve1);
1340 Soli[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]].resize(nve1);
1341 Soli_old[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]].resize(nve1);
1342 aRhs[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]].resize(nve1);
1343
1344 dofsAll.resize(0);
1345
1346 Jac.resize((nBlocks * dim * nve + nve1) * (nBlocks * dim * nve + nve1));
1347
1348 // ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1349 // coordinates, solutions, displacement, velocity dofs
1350
1351 solidmark.resize(nve);
1352
1353 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1354 vx[i].resize(nve);
1355 vx_hat[i].resize(nve);
1356 vx_old[i].resize(nve);
1357 }
1358
1359 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1360 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType2);
1361 // flag to know if the node "idof" lays on the fluid-solid interface
1362 solidmark[i] = mymsh->GetSolidMark(idof); // to check
1363
1364 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1365 for (unsigned k = 0; k < nBlocks; k++) {
1366 Soli[indexVAR[j + k * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j + k * dim]])(idof);
1367 Soli_old[indexVAR[j + k * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j + k * dim]])(idof);
1368 aRhs[indexVAR[j + k * dim]][i] = 0.;
1369 dofsVAR[j + k * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[j + k * dim], indexVAR[j + k * dim], i, iel);
1370 }
1371 vx_hat[j][i] = (*mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[j])(idof);
1372 }
1373 }
1374
1375 // pressure dofs
1376 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
1377 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType[nBlocks * dim]);
1378 dofsVAR[nBlocks * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[nBlocks * dim], indexVAR[nBlocks * dim], i, iel);
1379 Soli[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[nBlocks * dim]])(idof);
1380 Soli_old[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[nBlocks * dim]])(idof);
1381 aRhs[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] = 0.;
1382 }
1383
1384 // build dof ccomposition
1385 for (int idim = 0; idim < nBlocks * dim; idim++) {
1386 dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[idim].begin(), dofsVAR[idim].end());
1387 }
1388 dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[nBlocks * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[nBlocks * dim].end());
1389
1390 if (assembleMatrix) s.new_recording();
1391
1392
1393 for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
1394 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(j, iel, SolType2);
1395 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1396 vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim + meshIsCurrupted * 2 * dim]][j];
1397 vx_old[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim + meshIsCurrupted * 2 * dim]][j];
1398 }
1399 }
1400
1401 //Boundary integral
1402 {
1403
1404 std::vector < adept::adouble> normal(dim, 0);
1405 std::vector < double > normal_old(dim, 0);
1406
1407 // loop on faces
1408 for (unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber(iel); jface++) {
1409 std::vector< double > xx(dim, 0.);
1410
1411 // look for boundary faces
1412 if (myel->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) < 0) {
1413
1414 unsigned int face = - (mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) + 1);
1415 double tau = 0.;
1416 double tau_old = 0.;
1417 if ((!ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "PS", tau, face, time) &&
1418 !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "PS", tau_old, face, time - dt))
1419 && (tau != 0. || tau_old != 0.)) {
1420
1421 unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber(iel, jface, SolType2);
1422 const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType(iel, jface);
1423
1424 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1425 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
1426 unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(ilocal, iel, 2);
1427
1428 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1429 vx_face[idim][i] = (*mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[idim])(idof) + Soli[indexVAR[idim + meshIsCurrupted * 2 * dim]][ilocal]; //TODO
1430 vx_face_old[idim][i] = (*mymsh->GetTopology()->_Sol[idim])(idof) + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim + meshIsCurrupted * 2 * dim]][ilocal];
1431 }
1432 }
1433
1434 for (unsigned igs = 0; igs < mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); igs++) {
1435 mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face, igs, Weight, phi, gradphi, normal);
1436 mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face_old, igs, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, normal_old);
1437
1438 //phi1 =mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetPhi(igs);
1439 // *** phi_i loop ***
1440 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1441 adept::adouble value = - phi[i] * tau / rhof * Weight;
1442 double value_old = - phi_old[i] * tau_old / rhof * Weight_old;
1443 unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
1444
1445 for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1446 if ((!solidmark[ilocal])) {
1447 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += (theta * value + (1. - theta) * value_old) * normal[idim];
1448 }
1449 else { //if interface node it goes to solid
1450 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal] += (theta * value + (1. - theta) * value_old) * normal[idim];
1451 }
1452 }
1453 }
1454 }
1455 }
1456 }
1457 }
1458 }
1459
1460 // *** Gauss point loop ***
1461 double area = 1.;
1462
1463 for (unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++) {
1464 // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
1465 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx, ig, Weight, phi, gradphi, nablaphi);
1466 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_hat, ig, Weight_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat);
1467 mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_old, ig, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, nablaphi_old);
1468 phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi(ig);
1469
1470 if ( Weight.value() < 0. ) setIfCorrupted->set(iproc, 1.);
1471
1472 if (flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
1473 if (ig == 0) {
1474 double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight(ig);
1475 area = Weight_hat / GaussWeight;
1476
1477 if (iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
1478 area_elem_first->add(mymsh->processor_id(), area);
1479 area_elem_first->close();
1480 rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
1481 }
1482 }
1483
1484 Weight_nojac = Weight;// / area * 1.e-10;// * rapresentative_area;
1485
1486 //-----------------------------------------------------------------------//
1487 // for vein_valve mesh
1488 std::vector<double> xc(dim, 0.);
1489 //xc[0] = -0.001013; // vein_valve
1490 //xc[1] = 0.07000;
1491// xc[0] = -0.000286; // vein_valve_closed
1492// xc[1] = 0.07000;
1493//
1494 if (dim == 2) {
1495 xc[0] = -0.00025; // vein_valve_closed
1496 xc[1] = 0.07000;
1497 }
1498// else if (dim == 3){
1499// xc[0] = -0.008; // vein_valve_closed
1500// xc[1] = 0.0;
1501// }
1502 else if (dim == 3) {
1503 xc[0] = 0.0015; // vein_valve_closed
1504 xc[1] = 0.0;
1505 xc[2] = 0.01;
1506 }
1507
1508 double distance = 0.;
1509 for (unsigned k = 0; k < dim; k++) {
1510 distance += (vx_hat[k][ nve - 1] - xc[k]) * (vx_hat[k][nve - 1] - xc[k]);
1511 }
1512 distance = sqrt(distance);
1513 Weight_nojac *= 1. / (1 + 10000 * distance);
1514
1515 if (elementGroup == 16) Weight_nojac *= 100;
1516 //-----------------------------------------------------------------------//
1517 }
1518
1519 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1520 // displacement and velocity
1521 for (int i = 0; i < nBlocks * dim; i++) {
1522 SolVAR[i] = 0.;
1523 SolVAR_old[i] = 0.;
1524
1525 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1526 GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1527 GradSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
1528
1529 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1530 GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
1531 }
1532
1533 for (int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++) {
1534 NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1535 NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
1536 }
1537
1538 for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++) {
1539 SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1540 SolVAR_old[i] += phi_old[inode] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1541
1542 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1543 GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1544 GradSolVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_old[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1545
1546 GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1547 GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1548 }
1549 for (int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++) {
1550 NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1551 NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] += nablaphi_old[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1552 }
1553 }
1554 }
1555
1556 // pressure
1557 SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] = 0.;
1558
1559 for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++) {
1560 SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] += phi1[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][inode];
1561 }
1562
1563 // Lagrangian mesh velocity at t = time + dt/2
1564 std::vector < adept::adouble > meshVel(dim);
1565 std::vector < std::vector < adept::adouble > > GradMeshVel(dim);
1566
1567 for (unsigned i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1568 meshVel[i] = (SolVAR[i] - SolVAR_old[i]) / dt;
1569 GradMeshVel[i].resize(dim);
1570
1571 for (unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1572 GradMeshVel[i][j] = (GradSolVAR[i][j] - GradSolVAR_old[i][j]) / dt;
1573 }
1574 }
1575
1576 // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1577 //BEGIN FLUID and POROUS MEDIA ASSEMBLY ============
1578 if (flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3) {
1579
1580 std::vector < adept::adouble > a(dim);
1581 std::vector < adept::adouble > a_old(dim);
1582 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1583 a[i] = SolVAR[i + dim] - 0.*meshVel[i]; // TODO maybe we subtract meshVel[i] maybe not
1584 a_old[i] = SolVAR_old[i + dim] - 0.*meshVel[i];
1585 }
1586
1587 // speed
1588 adept::adouble aL2Norm = 0.;
1589 adept::adouble a_oldL2Norm = 0.;
1590 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1591 aL2Norm += a[i] * a[i];
1592 a_oldL2Norm += a_old[i] * a_old[i];
1593 }
1594 aL2Norm = sqrt(aL2Norm);
1595 a_oldL2Norm = sqrt(a_oldL2Norm);
1596
1597 double sqrtlambdak = (*mysolution->_Sol[indLmbd])(iel);
1598 adept::adouble tauSupg = 1. / (sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe);
1599 adept::adouble tauSupg_old = 1. / (sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe);
1600 adept::adouble Rek = aL2Norm / (4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe);
1601 adept::adouble Rek_old = a_oldL2Norm / (4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe);
1602
1603 if (Rek > 1.0e-15) {
1604 adept::adouble xiRek = (Rek >= 1.) ? 1. : Rek;
1605 tauSupg = xiRek / (aL2Norm * sqrtlambdak);
1606 }
1607
1608 if (Rek_old > 1.0e-15) {
1609 adept::adouble xiRek_old = (Rek_old >= 1.) ? 1. : Rek_old;
1610 tauSupg_old = xiRek_old / (a_oldL2Norm * sqrtlambdak);
1611 }
1612
1613 //std::cout << tauSupg.value() <<" " <<tauSupg_old.value()<<std::endl;
1614
1615
1616 std::vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg(nve, 0.);
1617 std::vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg_old(nve, 0.);
1618 //tauSupg=0;
1619 //tauSupg_old=0;
1620 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1621 for (unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1622 phiSupg[i] += ((SolVAR[j + dim] - meshVel[j]) * gradphi[i * dim + j]) * tauSupg; // * (!solidmark[i]) ;
1623 phiSupg_old[i] += ((SolVAR_old[j + dim] - meshVel[j]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + j]) * tauSupg_old; // * (!solidmark[i]);
1624 }
1625 }
1626
1627
1628 //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1629 {
1630 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1631
1632 //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
1633
1634
1635 if (!solidmark[i]) {
1636 adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1637 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1638 for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1639 //LapmapVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] ) * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim];
1640 LapmapVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] + 0.*GradSolVAR[jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1641 }
1642 }
1643
1644 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1645 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (- LapmapVAR[idim] * Weight_nojac);
1646 }
1647 }
1648
1649 //END residual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
1650
1651 if (flag_mat == 2) {
1652 //BEGIN residual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1653 adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1654 adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1655 adept::adouble LapStrong[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1656 adept::adouble LapStrong_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1657 adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1658 adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1659
1660 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1661 for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1662 unsigned kdim;
1663 if (idim == jdim) kdim = jdim;
1664 else if (1 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim; // xy
1665 else if (2 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim + 2; // xz
1666 else if (3 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim + 1; // yz
1667 //laplaciano debole
1668 LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1669 LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
1670 //laplaciano strong
1671 LapStrong[idim] += (NablaSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR[dim + jdim][kdim]) * phiSupg[i];
1672 LapStrong_old[idim] += (NablaSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][kdim]) * phiSupg_old[i];
1673
1674 AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
1675 + (0.*GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
1676 //) * phi[i];
1677 ) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i]);
1678
1679 AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
1680 + (0.*GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
1681 //) * phi_old[i];
1682 ) * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i]);
1683 }
1684 }
1685
1686 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1687
1688 adept::adouble timeDerivative = - (SolVAR[dim + idim] * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i]) * Weight
1689 - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i]) * Weight_old) / dt;
1690
1691 adept::adouble value = theta * (
1692 - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
1693 - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
1694 + IRe * LapStrong[idim]
1695 + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1696 ) * Weight; // at time t
1697
1698 adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * (
1699 - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
1700 - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
1701 + IRe * LapStrong_old[idim]
1702 + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1703 ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
1704
1705 if (!solidmark[i]) {
1706 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
1707 }
1708 else {
1709 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
1710 }
1711
1712 }
1713 //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1714 }
1715 else if (flag_mat == 3) {
1716 //BEGIN redidual Porous Media in moving domain
1717
1718
1719 adept::adouble speed = 0.;
1720 adept::adouble speed_old = 0.;
1721 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1722 speed += SolVAR[dim + idim] * SolVAR[dim + idim];
1723 speed_old += SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * SolVAR_old[dim + idim];
1724 }
1725 double eps = 1.0e-12;
1726 speed = sqrt(speed + eps);
1727 speed_old = sqrt(speed_old + eps);
1728 double DE = 0.;
1729 if (dim == 2) {
1730 DE = 0.0002; // AAA_thrombus_2D
1731 //DE = 0.00006; // turek2D
1732 }
1733 else if (dim == 3) {
1734 DE = 0.000112; // porous3D
1735 }
1736 double b = 4188;
1737 double a = 1452;
1738 double K = DE * IRe * rhof / b; // alpha = mu/b * De
1739 double C2 = 2 * a / (rhof * DE);
1740
1741
1742
1743
1744
1745// adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1746// adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1747// adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1748// adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1749//
1750// for(int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1751// for(int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1752//
1753// LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1754// LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
1755//
1756// AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
1757// + (GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
1758// ) * phi[i];
1759//
1760// AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
1761// + (GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
1762// ) * phi_old[i];
1763// }
1764// }
1765
1766 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1767
1768// adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
1769// - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
1770
1771 adept::adouble value = theta * (
1772// - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
1773// - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
1774 //- SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * phi[i]
1775 - (SolVAR[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * (IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i])
1776 + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1777 ) * Weight; // at time t
1778
1779 adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * (
1780// - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
1781// - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
1782 //- SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed_old ) * phi_old[i]
1783 - (SolVAR_old[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * (IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed) * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i])
1784 + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1785 ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
1786
1787 if (!solidmark[i]) {
1788 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value + value_old;
1789 }
1790 else {
1791 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += value + value_old;
1792 }
1793
1794 }
1795 //END redidual Porous Media in moving domain
1796 }
1797
1798 if (auxDisp) {
1799 //BEGIN auxiliary displacement equation
1800 adept::adouble LapAuxVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1801
1802 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1803 for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1804 LapAuxVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim + 2 * dim][jdim] + 0. * GradSolVAR[jdim + 2 * dim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1805 }
1806 }
1807
1808 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1809 aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( meshIsCurrupted * 1.0e-1 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + 0 * ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi[i] ) * Weight_nojac;
1810 }
1811// for (int idim = 1; idim < dim; idim++) {
1812// aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( meshIsCurrupted * 1.0e-1 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + 0 * ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi[i] ) * Weight_nojac;
1813// }
1814// for (int idim = 1; idim < dim; idim++) {
1815// aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( meshIsCurrupted * 1.0e-1 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + 0 * ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi[i] ) * Weight_nojac;
1816// }
1817
1818// adept::adouble LapAuxVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1819//
1820// for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1821// for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1822// LapAuxVAR[idim] += GradSolhatVAR[idim + 2 * dim][jdim] * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim];
1823// }
1824// }
1825//
1826// for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1827// aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( 1.0e-10 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi_hat[i] ) * Weight_hat;
1828// }
1829
1830
1831 //END auxiliary displacement equation
1832 }
1833
1834 }
1835 }
1836 //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1837
1838
1839
1840
1841
1842 //BEGIN continuity block
1843 {
1844 adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
1845
1846 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1847 div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
1848 }
1849
1850 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
1851 aRhs[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] += - (-phi1[i] * div_vel) * Weight;
1852 }
1853 }
1854 //END continuity block ===========================
1855 }
1856 //END FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
1857
1858 //*******************************************************************************************************
1859
1860 //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
1861 else {
1862 //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
1863 //physical quantity
1864 adept::adouble J_hat;
1865 adept::adouble J_hat1;
1866 double J_hat_old;
1867 adept::adouble I_e;
1868 double I_e_old;
1869 adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
1870 adept::adouble Cauchy_old[3][3];
1871 double Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
1872
1873
1874
1875
1876 if (solid_model == 0) { // Saint-Venant
1877 adept::adouble e[3][3];
1878 double e_old[3][3];
1879
1880 //computation of the stress tensor
1881 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1882 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1883 e[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i]);
1884 e_old[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR_old[j][i]);
1885 }
1886 }
1887
1888 I_e = 0;
1889 I_e_old = 0;
1890
1891 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1892 I_e += e[i][i];
1893 I_e_old += e_old[i][i];
1894 }
1895
1896 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1897 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1898 //incompressible
1899 Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
1900 Cauchy_old[i][j] = 2 * mus * e_old[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e_old * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
1901 //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
1902 }
1903 }
1904 }
1905
1906 else { // hyperelastic non linear material
1907
1908 adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
1909 adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
1910
1911 double I1_B_old = 0.;
1912 double I2_B_old = 0.;
1913
1914 adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1915 adept::adouble F1[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1916 adept::adouble B[3][3];
1917
1918 double F_old[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1919 double B_old[3][3];
1920
1921 for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1922 for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1923 F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
1924 F1[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i + 2 * dim][j];
1925 F_old[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j];
1926 }
1927 }
1928
1929 J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
1930 - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
1931
1932 J_hat1 = F1[0][0] * F1[1][1] * F1[2][2] + F1[0][1] * F1[1][2] * F1[2][0] + F1[0][2] * F1[1][0] * F1[2][1]
1933 - F1[2][0] * F1[1][1] * F1[0][2] - F1[2][1] * F1[1][2] * F1[0][0] - F1[2][2] * F1[1][0] * F1[0][1];
1934
1935 J_hat_old = F_old[0][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[2][2] + F_old[0][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[2][0]
1936 + F_old[0][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[2][1] - F_old[2][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[0][2]
1937 - F_old[2][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[0][0] - F_old[2][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[0][1];
1938
1939
1940 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1941 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1942 B[I][J] = 0.;
1943 B_old[I][J] = 0.;
1944
1945 for (int K = 0; K < 3; ++K) {
1946 //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
1947 B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
1948 B_old[I][J] += F_old[I][K] * F_old[J][K];
1949 }
1950 }
1951 }
1952
1953 if (solid_model <= 4) { // Neo-Hookean
1954 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
1955 I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
1956
1957 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1958 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1959 if (1 == solid_model) { //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
1960 Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) - mus / 3.*I1_B * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1961 Cauchy_old[I][J] = mus * (B_old[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) - mus / 3.*I1_B_old * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1962 }
1963
1964// else if ( 2 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus/J_hat*B[I][J]
1965// -mus/J_hat*SolVAR[2*dim]*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
1966// else if ( 3 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J])/J_hat
1967// + lambda/J_hat*log(J_hat)*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
1968// else if ( 4 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - I1_B*Id2th[I][J]/3.)/pow(J_hat,5./3.)
1969// + lambda*(J_hat-1.)*Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
1970//
1971 }
1972 }
1973 }
1974 else if (5 == solid_model) { //Mooney-Rivlin
1975 adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2])
1976 - B[0][1] * (B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0])
1977 + B[0][2] * (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]);
1978
1979 double detB_old = B_old[0][0] * (B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[2][1] * B_old[1][2])
1980 - B_old[0][1] * (B_old[2][2] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0])
1981 + B_old[0][2] * (B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1]);
1982
1983 adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
1984 double invdetB_old = 1. / detB_old;
1985 adept::adouble invB[3][3];
1986 double invB_old[3][3];
1987
1988 invB[0][0] = (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
1989 invB[1][0] = - (B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
1990 invB[2][0] = (B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
1991 invB[0][1] = - (B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
1992 invB[1][1] = (B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
1993 invB[2][1] = - (B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2]) * invdetB;
1994 invB[0][2] = (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
1995 invB[1][2] = - (B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
1996 invB[2][2] = (B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
1997
1998 invB_old[0][0] = (B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1]) * invdetB_old;
1999 invB_old[1][0] = - (B_old[0][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][1]) * invdetB_old;
2000 invB_old[2][0] = (B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[1][1]) * invdetB_old;
2001 invB_old[0][1] = - (B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0]) * invdetB_old;
2002 invB_old[1][1] = (B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][0]) * invdetB_old;
2003 invB_old[2][1] = - (B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][2]) * invdetB_old;
2004 invB_old[0][2] = (B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1]) * invdetB_old;
2005 invB_old[1][2] = - (B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][1]) * invdetB_old;
2006 invB_old[2][2] = (B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][1]) * invdetB_old;
2007
2008
2009 I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
2010 I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
2011 - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
2012
2013 I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
2014 I2_B_old = B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] + B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] + B_old[2][2] * B_old[0][0]
2015 - B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][2];
2016
2017 //double C1 = mus / 3.;
2018 double C1 = (elementGroup == 15) ? mus1 / 3. : mus / 3.;
2019 double C2 = C1 / 2.;
2020
2021 for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
2022 for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
2023 Cauchy[I][J] = 2.* (C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J])
2024 //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
2025 - 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
2026
2027 Cauchy_old[I][J] = 2.* (C1 * B_old[I][J] - C2 * invB_old[I][J])
2028 //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B_old - C2 * I2_B_old) * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
2029 - 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
2030
2031 }
2032 }
2033
2034 }
2035 }
2036
2037 //END build Cauchy Stress in moving domain
2038
2039 //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
2040 {
2041 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
2042
2043 //BEGIN redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
2044 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
2045 aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += - phi[i] * ((-SolVAR[idim] + SolVAR_old[idim]) / dt +
2046 (theta * SolVAR[dim + idim] + (1. - theta) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim])
2047 ) * Weight_hat;
2048 }
2049
2050 //END redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
2051
2052 //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
2053 adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
2054 adept::adouble CauchyDIR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
2055
2056 for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
2057 for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
2058 CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
2059 CauchyDIR_old[idim] += gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy_old[idim][jdim];
2060 }
2061 }
2062
2063 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
2064
2065 adept::adouble timeDerivative = - (rhos * SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
2066 - rhos * SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old) / dt;
2067
2068 adept::adouble value = theta * (rhos * phi[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
2069 - CauchyDIR[idim] // stress
2070 ) * Weight; // at time t
2071
2072 adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * (rhos * phi_old[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
2073 - CauchyDIR_old[idim] // stress
2074 ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
2075
2076 aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
2077 }
2078
2079 //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
2080
2081
2082 if (auxDisp) {
2083 //BEGIN auxiliary displacement equation
2084 adept::adouble LapAuxVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
2085
2086 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
2087 for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
2088 LapAuxVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim + 2 * dim][jdim] + 0 * GradSolVAR[jdim + 2 * dim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
2089 }
2090 }
2091
2092// for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
2093// aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( 1.0e-8 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi_hat[i] ) * Weight;
2094// }
2095
2096 for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
2097 aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( meshIsCurrupted * LapAuxVAR[idim] + factordxi[idim] * ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi[i] ) * Weight;
2098 }
2099// for (int idim = 1; idim < dim; idim++) {
2100// aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( meshIsCurrupted * LapAuxVAR[idim] + factordy * ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi[i] ) * Weight;
2101// }
2102
2103
2104
2105
2106// adept::adouble LapAuxVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
2107//
2108// for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
2109// for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
2110// LapAuxVAR[idim] += GradSolhatVAR[idim + 2 * dim][jdim] * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim];
2111// }
2112// }
2113//
2114// for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
2115// aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( 1.0e-8 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi_hat[i] ) * Weight_hat;
2116// }
2117 //END auxiliary displacement equation
2118 }
2119
2120 }
2121 }
2122 //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
2123
2124 //BEGIN continuity block
2125 {
2126 for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
2127 if (!penalty) {
2128 if (0 == solid_model) {
2129 aRhs[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] += - (-phi1[i] * (I_e + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim])) * Weight_hat;
